tat. P\u00e5 Hitra er \u00abInn p\u00e5 tunet\u00bb tatt i bruk for \u00e5 f\u00e5 arbeidsledige og folk p\u00e5 attf\u00f8ring tilbake i vanlig arbeid."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "ec430d28372a941d5a31e304403b6964ae04e31a9d141fb2fb5e6dafa89d5212"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-10-19T15:27:50.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "\u00d8RLAND: Skoletilbud gjennom prosjektet \u00abInn p\u00e5 tunet\u00bb er blitt en suksess. N\u00e5 skal ogs\u00e5 arbeidsledige, syke, senile og rusmisbrukere f\u00e5 et tilbud i fj\u00f8set."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/22ac59ebb28292a81dd0a7ee3e115fdb904fd7c5.jpg?598c5b8f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Helsefarm inn p\u00e5 tunet -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "22ac59ebb28292a81dd0a7ee3e115fdb904fd7c5"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kommune", "videreg\u00e5ende skole", "tiltak", "lokale tiltak", "tunet", "tilbud"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["fosen", "torhild aabergsbotten", "midtre gauldal og \u00f8rland", "aetat", "frammig\u00e5rden"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "brekstad", "hitra", "tr\u00f8ndelag", "midtre gauldal", "mer\u00e5ker", "\u00f8rland"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["hanne k. h\u00f8ys\u00e6ther", "kari fr\u00f8seth", "bj\u0